threads.title: 820-00165 PM_SLP_S4_L  is sitting at 0.915V
threads.message: hello guys ... Please I need help on this one .. have got an 820-00165 that is missing PM_SLP_S4_L , however its not completely missing but sitting at 0.9V .... Other rails other than the S4 are present . any hint guys ?

threads.title: 820-00165 PM_SLP_S4_L  is sitting at 0.915V
threads.message:
PM_SLP_S4_L enables S3 state!
So check other previous signals, if you do no get into S4 yet.

threads.title: 820-00165 PM_SLP_S4_L  is sitting at 0.915V
threads.message: Thank you for your response ... Resolved
